  <summary date="2021-07-06T18:56:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Helping Homeless Veterans Act of 2021

 This bill permanently extends the following Department of Veterans Affairs programs and services:

 homeless veterans reintegration programs, financial assistance for supportive services for very low-income veteran families in permanent housing, a grant program for homeless veterans with special needs, treatment and rehabilitation for seriously mentally ill and homeless veterans, housing assistance for homeless veterans, and the Advisory Committee on Homeless Veterans.</summary>
